{"tid":1140691,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"藍斯淚灑球場","createTime":"2019-05-06T04:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T05:00:35.000Z","uid":122167,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"51da2153fd6519e5ab825668151884975107bab5","tid":1140691,"uid":122167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:22:46.000Z","msg":"與白禮頓一戰，阿仙奴因為1-1的比數已徹底丟掉了今季爭四的希望。而在這場比賽結束後，兵工廠球迷們還迎來了一次傷感的告別儀式。<br />\n<br />\n賽後，阿仙奴全隊列隊為藍斯（A.Ramsey）、施治（P.Cech）、韋碧克（D.Welbeck）告別，而為兵工廠效力了長達11年的藍斯在全場熱烈的氛圍中也難以控制自己的情緒，激動地在這個一路見證了自己成長的地方留下了眼淚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2fTwvoL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2fTwvoL.gif&h=3619fa01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uheomu8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUheomu8.gif&h=70eca127&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2670d5a6e161a91a2ca31cac5b5c2b784201f4ef","tid":1140691,"uid":29993,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"躝啦25"},{"pid":"4cfce9eaca0133b63951b3e5e88924b5d65d9cf4","tid":1140691,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:00:35.000Z","msg":"韋迫去邊呀？"}]}